Dahua ASI7XXX: Versions prior to v1.000.0000009.0.R.220620
Dahua IPC-HDBW2XXX: Versions prior to v2.820.0000000.48.R.220614
Dahua IPC-HX2XXX: Versions Prior to v2.820.0000000.48.R.220614

